## CheckListBox
  
### Features

* Support to group items in CheckListBox
* Support to sort items in CheckListBox
* UI Virtualization support is provided
* All items can be selected at once using 'Selected All' item.

### Behavior Changes

* In earlier version, all checked items will be in selected state. Hear onwards, only focused item will be selected.
* `SelectionChanged` event will be fired based selection behavior changes explained above, use 'SelectedItems.CollectionChanged` event to notify about changes in checked items.



